| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2874 — Recovery Inhibition (malas)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cfd23144-f191-5e39-9d15-8d4750a85ea4"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
